          "METHOD": [
            {
              "pointer": "",
              "coded_information": [
                "TOF",
                "PHD"
              ],
              "free_text": [
                " Cross sections were measured for two",
                "different paths and detector assemblies (sets I and",
                "II). For each event the digital output was on-line",
                "processed by application of a pulse-height weighting",
                "scheme. The efficiency of the capture gamma ray",
                "detector was obtained by the application of the",
                "saturated resonance method to the 238U resonance at",
                "6.7 eV. The shape of the neutron spectrum was",
                "obtained with 10BF3 ionization chamber for set I, and",
                "6Li glass detector for set II."
              ]
            }
          ],
